==============================================================================
DATASET LICENSE
==============================================================================

The dataset and anonymized samples provided in this repository are released
under separate terms for research purposes only:

1. RESEARCH USE ONLY: The data may only be used for non-commercial academic
   research purposes.

2. ATTRIBUTION: Any use of the data must cite the original publication:

   Sergeev, D. (2025). Multimodal Talent Discovery in Children Using
   Calibrated Baselines. DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.17941256 (Preprint available on Zenodo)

3. NO REDISTRIBUTION: The full dataset may not be redistributed without
   written permission from Talents.Kids.

4. PRIVACY PROTECTION: All data has been anonymized to comply with GDPR and
   COPPA regulations. Researchers must maintain this anonymization and must
   not attempt to de-anonymize participants.

5. IRB APPROVAL: Access to the full dataset requires active IRB approval for
   human subjects research and a signed Data Use Agreement with Talents.Kids.

For questions about dataset access or commercial use, contact:
ds@talents.kids

